          "date": "2012-11-16 07:33:55.000000000",
          "tz": 540
        },
        "subject": "LU-2306 obdclass: solve an unexpected behaviors of class_decref",
        "message": "LU-2306 obdclass: solve an unexpected behaviors of class_decref\n\nWhen LOV obd_device on a client node is registered with target OSCs\n\n- marge the two if-statements in class_decref() in order for\n  class_decref() not to call obd_precleanup and unlink the same\n  self export multiple times\n- unlink a self export and wait for releasing it in class_cleanup()\n  to let class_detach() to put the last obd_refcount and to detach\n  obd_device from the obd_devs list\n- marge OBD_CLEANUP_SELF_EXP into OBD_CLEANUP_EXPORTS because of\n  the change in class_decref() in this patch\n\nSigned-off-by: Hiroya Nozaki <nozaki.hiroya@jp.fujitsu.com>\nChange-Id: Ied9e8e3acfb1b1e261079c549f1f7e39445d715f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b1_8"
    }
